        },
        {
          "title": "Theological Significance: Shabbat's Kedushah of Time Precedes and Supersedes the Kedushah of the Mikdash's Space",
          "display_title": "Shabbat Supremacy",
          "timestamp": "28:03"
        },
        {
          "title": "The Accessibility Principle: Time's Kedushah Is Available to All, While Space's Kedushah Has Limited Access",
